<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="envy-vt">envy <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'envi/    美 /'envi/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>妒忌；羡慕：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>envy sb (doing) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They envy him his good fortune. 
他们羡慕他的好运气。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I envy you having such a close family. 
我羡慕你有这么亲密的一个家庭。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— I'm going to San Francisco for a couple of days.
— I really <strong><em>_</em></strong>__ (羡慕) you.  （2012 浙江改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. envy  </p></div>